 Hydras smiled. "Well then let us head out to the enemy and beat the slag 
outta them. His fire wings spread as he pulled his swords. "Quilldart 
nightshade Quickstrike and Strika should stay here and guard the base. If 
anything should come at us let me know immediatly. He turned and left walking 
down the ramp. His eyes fixed in the direction of the maximal base. Proto and 
Destructor stood beside him eager for battle.

--part1_120.188d159b.2aed5ecb_boundary
